<subSubSection type="description">
<paragraph pageNumber="484">Major: antennal scrobes present; extensive rugoreticulum covers all the dorsal head surface from the level of the anterior margin of the eyes to the occiput, except for a median strip and the antennal scrobes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="484">Measurements (mm) Holotype major: HW 0.54, HL 0.60, SL 0.30, EL 0.06, PW 0.32.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="484">Paratype minor: HW 0.36, HL 0.38, SL 0.30, EL 0.06, PW 0.22.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="484">color Major: body light reddish yellow (&quot;orange&quot;), appendages light yellow.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageNumber="484">Minor: concolorous pale yellow.</paragraph>
